data.description: Situated in the coveted Wexford Village, discover a 3-bed, 2.5-bath residence that captures the essence of comfortable living with a contemporary touch! Entering this home, you're immediately taken by its open layout, graced with high ceilings, neutral palette, and durable tile flooring, creating a serene ambiance perfect for entertainment. The kitchen boasts tile counters, modern recessed lighting, classic paneled cabinets, built-in appliances, a convenient pantry, and a peninsula with a breakfast bar. The main bedroom is generously sized, featuring a walk-in closet and a well-appointed private bathroom designed for comfort. Extending the living space outdoors, the back patio provides a cozy retreat perfect for morning coffee. Strategically located near bus stops, restaurants, and shopping. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity!
